      </li>
      <li class="lessons--item-header">
        <hr />
      </li>
      <li class="lessons--item">
        <img class="span-2-full" src="/images/img_module_11/m11_8.png" alt="" />
      </li>
      <li class="lessons--item-header">
        <hr />
      </li>
      <li class="lessons--item">
        <img class="span-2-full" src="/images/img_module_11/m11_9.png" alt="" />
      </li>
      <li class="lessons--item-header">
        <h1 class="primary-text text-center">
          How to find the equation of the tangent line and normal line | Basic
          Calculus
        </h1>
        <hr />
      </li>

      <li class="video-container lessons--item">
        <iframe
          class="span-2-full"
          src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/DeByl5uQD1I"
          title="YouTube video player"
          frameborder="0"
          allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
          allowfullscreen></iframe>
      </li>
      <li class="lessons--item-header">
        <h1 class="primary-text text-center">
          Slope and Equation of Normal & Tangent Line of Curve at Given Point -
          Calculus Function & Graphs
        </h1>
        <hr />
      </li>

      <li class="video-container lessons--item">
        <iframe
          class="span-2-full"
          src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/7EFYoQ6H7Tw"
          title="YouTube video player"
          frameborder="0"
          allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
          allowfullscreen></iframe>
      </li>
      <li class="lessons--item">
        <div class="switch span-2-full clicked">
          <input type="checkbox" id="switch-btn11" />
          <label for="switch-btn11">
            <span class="switch-label secondary-text">Mark as complete</span>
          </label>
        </div>

        <div id="confirm-box11" class="confirm-box">
          <p class="secondary-text">Check complete module?</p>
          <button id="confirm-yes-btn11" class="btn btn--confirm">Yes</button>
          <button id="confirm-no-btn11" class="btn btn--deny">No</button>
        </div>
        <div id="overlay11" class="overlay"></div>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </main>
